        "MPON sends the dismissal",
        "MPOO reviews the dismissal",
        "exclusivegateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以起点是MPON发送解雇通知，接着MPOO审核，然后到一个判断节点。不管是反对还是确认，最后都要汇合到一起结束，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
