    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，两个分支最后要汇合。反对的话是\"MPOO opposes the dismissal\"，确认的话是\"MPOO confirmes the dismissal\"，注意确认那边拼写有点问题，应该是confirms，不过先按业务逻辑来画。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MPOO opposes the dismissal",
        "MPOO confirmes the dismissal"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把流程画出来了：从开始节点，到MPON发送解雇，MPOO审核，然后分支到反对或确认，两个分支汇合后结束。您看一下这个结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
