      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，确认那个节点的拼写需要修正，是\"confirms\"不是\"confirmes\"，另外汇合的那个网关位置要确认一下，反对分支和确认分支都要连到同一个结束网关。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MPOO confirmes the dismissal",
        "exclusivegateway"
